title: Person of Interest - 3x21 - Beta - The ending
author: George Finch
comment: The world definitely needs people like Reese and Finch.
Greer&Finch scenes from 4x22 are my favorite scenes from Person of Interest. They were both right in everything they said and I really admire Nolan's acting.
"We lost finch, which mean we lost everything "
I hope that they show more of Nathan and Finch, maybe how they got together.
